title: Various Artists - Indie 69 September 2013 New Music Monthly
description:
The Indie69 New Music Monthly Playlist is a collection of new and mostly new
tracks with an emphasis on independent artists (but there are many exceptions).
69 tracks a month. 

My best attempt is always made to get the highest quality possible (320kbps
usually) , and most artists/labels want a possible fan's first experience with
their music to be the best quality possible. However, this is not always the
case, so there will always be a few 128kbps tracks. 

I hope you enjoy the September, 2013 playlist and I will see you (earlier?) in
October. 

Thanks to everyone for the thanks and the tracks.

You can find me at @indie69 . 

The blog is still dead until I can pay for it.
